beniel.es Ayuntamiento de Beniel is the local government authority of the town of Beniel, located in the Region of Murcia, Spain.It is responsible for the administration and governance of the municipality. The organization provides public and administrative services to local residents. Its duties include population registration and issuing official certificates and documents. It manages the municipal budget, local taxes, and public spending. The municipality oversees urban planning, infrastructure, and public maintenance. It coordinates social services, cultural initiatives, and sports programs. The local government organizes and supports community events and public celebrations. sasi.vn - SASI (Saigon Auto Supporting Industry JSC) is a Vietnamese industrial manufacturing company operating via the domain sasi.vn, focused on large-scale OEM production.SASI is a long-established manufacturer, founded in the 1970s, with production facilities located in Ho Chi Minh City (Cu Chi Industrial Park), which is an important industrial zone for heavy and precision manufacturing in Vietnam.The company’s core activity is OEM and supporting industry manufacturing, meaning it produces metal parts, components, and assemblies strictly according to customer specifications rather than selling consumer products under its own brand.SASI plays a critical role in automotive and industrial supply chains, supplying components used in vehicles, motorcycles, industrial machinery, and selected medical and technical equipment.
